 x^{n - 1} + x^{n - 2} + \cdots + x + 1 = \left(x - w\right)\left(x - w^{2}\right)\ldots\left(x - w^{n - 1}\right) 
 \sin\left(\pi \over n\right)\sin\left(2\pi \over n\right)\ldots \sin\left(\left[n-1\right]\pi \over n\right) = {n \over 2^{n - 1}} 
 w=e^{i\frac{2\pi}{n}}=z^2, 
 z=e^{i\frac{\pi}{n}} 
 \sin\left(\frac{\pi}{n}\right)\ldots\sin\left(\frac{(n-1)\pi}{n}\right)=\frac{n}{2^{n-1}}. 
\sin z = \frac{e^{zi}-e^{-zi}}{2i}
\text{RHS}
\prod_{j=1}^{n-1}\sin\frac{j\pi}{n}=\prod_{j=1}^{n-1}\left[\frac{e^{ji\pi/n}-e^{-ji\pi/n}}{2i}\right]
\prod_{j=1}^{n-1}\left[\frac{e^{ji\pi/n}-e^{-ji\pi/n}}{2i}\right]=\prod_{j=1}^{n-1}\left[\frac{e^{-ji\pi/n}\left(e^{2ji\pi/n}-1\right)}{2i}\right]\text{ } (*)
